## 4. Pricing Page Experiments

**Structure tests:**
- 2 tiers vs. 3 tiers vs. 4 tiers
- Monthly default vs. annual default
- Show savings percentage for annual vs. don't
- Feature comparison table vs. feature lists per tier
- "Most popular" badge on a tier vs. no badge

**Price display tests:**
- Per month vs. per year vs. per user/month
- Rounded pricing ($50) vs. charm pricing ($49)
- Show crossed-out original price vs. don't
- Calculator/slider for usage-based pricing
- "Starting at" pricing vs. exact pricing

**CTA tests:**
- "Start Free Trial" on all tiers vs. tier-specific CTAs
- "Contact Sales" on enterprise vs. self-serve signup
- Money-back guarantee messaging near price vs. away from price

