## 5. Form Experiments

**Length tests:**
- Email only vs. email + name vs. full form
- Single-page form vs. multi-step form
- Progressive disclosure (ask more later) vs. all fields upfront

**Design tests:**
- Inline labels vs. floating labels vs. above-field labels
- Single column vs. two column layout
- With progress indicator vs. without
- Form on page vs. form in modal

**Microcopy tests:**
- Privacy reassurance near email field vs. none
- Helper text below fields vs. placeholder text
- Error messages: inline vs. top of form
- "No credit card required" messaging vs. none

